## Newsbeuter configuration file.
refresh-on-startup yes
auto-reload yes
reload-time 1
reload-threads 2
browser icecat
download-path "~/Downloads/Podcasts"
feed-sort-order name
max-downloads 1
notify-always yes
notify-format "Newsbeuter: %n unread articles within %f unread feeds"
notify-program notify-send
player mpv
cleanup-on-quit yes
show-read-articles yes
show-read-feeds yes

## Keybindings
bind-key R reload-all
bind-key "RIGHT" select-tag
bind-key "ENTER" open

## Hide articles matching
ignore-article "*" "title =~ \"Sponsor\""
ignore-article "*" "title =~ \"Advertisement\""
ignore-mode "display"

## Formatting & colorisation 
color background red default
color listnormal white default 
color listfocus white default
color info white default
color listfocus_unread red default
color listnormal_unread red default
